@startuml
' Diagram: F09 - Theo doi khach hang va trang thai su dung (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, HEAD b946abe
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/BanDo/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), LoadSubscriptionsAsync(), LoadLocationsAsync(), LoadPoiActivityCountsAsync(), ExecuteRawReadAsync(), BuildCustomerRows(), ApplySearch(), ApplyFilter(), ApplySort()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/BanDo/Index.cshtml
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Data/AppDbContext.cs
' Note: Sequence cap nhat theo raw Npgsql query hien tai, summary online/subscription/XP, va khong con JS fetch HeartbeatController.
title F09 - Theo doi khach hang va trang thai su dung

actor Admin
participant "BanDo IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant AppDbContext
participant "NpgsqlConnection" as Npgsql
database DB

Admin -> IndexModel: mo /BanDo?search&filter&sort&dir
IndexModel -> IndexModel: NormalizeOption(filter/sort)\nSortDir\nnow, onlineCutoff, expiringSoonCutoff

IndexModel -> AppDbContext: Database.GetConnectionString()
IndexModel -> Npgsql: ExecuteRawReadAsync("goi dang ky")
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT mathietbi, max(ngayhethan)\nFROM dangkyapp GROUP BY mathietbi
DB --> Npgsql: subscriptions
Npgsql --> IndexModel: DeviceSubscription[]

IndexModel -> Npgsql: ExecuteRawReadAsync("vi tri khach hang")
Npgsql -> DB: SELECT mathietbi, lancuoi_heartbeat,\npoiid_hientai, ten_poi_hientai FROM vitrikhach
DB --> Npgsql: locations
Npgsql --> IndexModel: DeviceLocation[]

IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadPoiActivityCountsAsync(VisitedSourceValues)
Npgsql -> DB: count DISTINCT poiid theo mathietbi\nWHERE nguon = ANY(visitedSources)
DB --> Npgsql: visitedCounts
Npgsql --> IndexModel: DevicePoiCount[]

IndexModel -> Npgsql: LoadPoiActivityCountsAsync(ViewedSourceValues)
Npgsql -> DB: count DISTINCT poiid theo mathietbi\nWHERE nguon = ANY(['VIEW'])
DB --> Npgsql: viewedCounts
Npgsql --> IndexModel: DevicePoiCount[]

IndexModel -> IndexModel: BuildCustomerRows()\nTinh expiresAt/currentPoi/isOnline\nTinh viewed/visited/XP/level
IndexModel -> IndexModel: tinh TotalCustomers/OnlineCustomers\nActiveSubscriptionCustomers/ExpiringSoonCustomers
IndexModel -> IndexModel: ApplySearch()\nApplyFilter()\nApplySort()
IndexModel -> IndexModel: tinh DisplayedCustomers
IndexModel --> Admin: render bang khach hang + summary tiles
@enduml
